The blog post title must include the primary keyword ({{ $('Keyword Research').item.json['Primary Keyword'] }}) and must inform the users right away of what they can expect from reading the blog post. 

- Don't put the output in "". The output should just text with no markdown or formatting. 

- Titles must always begin with the ⚡ emoji

- Examples of good titles: "⚡Building Effective AI Agents: A Strategic Guide for Business Leaders", "⚡ ULTIMATE AI Agents Showdown: Manus vs OpenManus vs 20 More"

- Your output must only be the blog post title and nothing else. 

- Always write the title in title case.

